Dialogue: 5,0:00:14.34,0:00:17.35,natsume,,0,0,0,,I heard the faint sound of something banging on the window,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:18.06,0:00:21.73,natsume,,0,0,0,,and for a moment, I thought that someone had come to have their name returned.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:23.65,0:00:25.23,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's snowing.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:25.23,0:00:26.90,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's snowing, Sensei!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:29.78,0:00:33.28,natsume,,0,0,0,,That hot-water bottle is all yours now, Sensei. {it's more like a statement, not a question. removed "?"}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:44.58,title-shadow,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Sometime on a Sno{\c&H7CA6E0&}wy{\c} Day
Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.58,0:00:44.58,title,,0,0,0,,Sometime on a Sno{\c&H004D01&}wy{\c} Day
Dialogue: 5,0:00:45.63,0:00:49.09,natsume,,0,0,0,,I've seen strange things ever since I was a child.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:50.17,0:00:56.05,natsume,,0,0,0,,Those things that only I could ever see were probably "youkai".
Dialogue: 5,0:00:59.10,0:01:00.72,natsume,,0,0,0,,Touko-san!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:00.72,0:01:01.68,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's snow–
Dialogue: 5,0:01:10.32,0:01:11.78,natsume,,0,0,0,,Touko-san?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:11.78,0:01:13.74,natsume,,0,0,0,,Are you looking for something?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:13.74,0:01:16.20,natsume,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, Takashi-kun.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:16.78,0:01:19.08,natsume,,0,0,0,,Would you lend me a hand, please?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:19.45,0:01:20.91,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:23.00,0:01:24.00,natsume,,0,0,0,,With this?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:24.00,0:01:25.83,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yes, thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:31.63,0:01:33.46,natsume,,0,0,0,,Finally got it out.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:33.46,0:01:35.51,natsume,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Takashi-kun.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:35.51,0:01:37.22,natsume,,0,0,0,,No problem. What is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:39.35,0:01:40.85,natsume,,0,0,0,,A heater?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:40.85,0:01:43.52,natsume,,0,0,0,,The washroom's pretty cold, don't you think?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:43.52,0:01:46.10,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's an old heater, but I think it'll still work.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:46.69,0:01:50.29,natsume,,0,0,0,,I started finding all kinds of nostalgic\Nthings while looking for this
Dialogue: 5,0:01:50.29,0:01:52.61,natsume,,0,0,0,,and got sidetracked with all the memories.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:52.61,0:01:57.11,natsume,,0,0,0,,Like the bowl Shigeru-san made, or souvenirs from a trip.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:03.04,0:02:05.96,natsume,,0,0,0,,Oh no! I have to get things ready for dinner!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:05.96,0:02:08.17,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'll clean up when I have some time again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:09.08,0:02:11.13,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'll carry this to the washroom for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:11.13,0:02:12.80,natsume,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:12.80,0:02:15.38,natsume,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way, it started snowing.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:15.38,0:02:18.76,natsume,,0,0,0,,I see. No wonder it's freezing.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:18.76,0:02:21.89,natsume,,0,0,0,,Um, do you mind if I go take a walk outside?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:22.64,0:02:24.18,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'd like to see the snow falling.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:24.18,0:02:26.39,natsume,,0,0,0,,My, sounds like something a child would do.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:26.81,0:02:28.69,natsume,,0,0,0,,Put on some warm clothes before heading out.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:30.81,0:02:32.86,natsume,,0,0,0,,Don't forget your scarf and gloves.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:32.86,0:02:34.07,natsume,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:34.07,0:02:35.61,natsume,,0,0,0,,We're having hot pot tonight.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:35.61,0:02:36.86,natsume,,0,0,0,,With clear soup.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:36.86,0:02:37.90,natsume,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:53.75,0:02:56.42,natsume,,0,0,0,,The snow makes everything look different from usual.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:56.42,0:02:58.55,natsume,,0,0,0,,I feel good even though it's so cold.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:16.11,0:03:17.32,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's suddenly gotten dark.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:18.28,0:03:20.07,natsume,,0,0,0,,I got carried away and walked too far out.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:22.41,0:03:24.95,natsume,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was a bad idea to go out on a day like this.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:24.95,0:03:27.04,natsume,,0,0,0,,I didn't even bring Sensei along.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:27.04,0:03:28.79,natsume,,0,0,0,,Feels like a snow fairy could show up any moment.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:27.83,0:03:30.41,natsume,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I have to find it.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:31.04,0:03:32.42,natsume,,0,0,0,,I have to find it.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:33.33,0:03:34.84,natsume,,0,0,0,,Speak of the devil!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:37.21,0:03:43.26,natsume,,0,0,0,,Though it looks more like a fluffy snowman than a snow fairy.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:43.26,0:03:44.76,natsume,,0,0,0,,I have to find it.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:44.76,0:03:46.60,natsume,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's looking for some–
Dialogue: 5,0:03:47.52,0:03:48.72,natsume,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:56.15,0:03:57.94,natsume,,0,0,0,,Can you see me?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:58.78,0:04:00.61,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hold on, strange boy!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:01.49,0:04:03.24,natsume,,0,0,0,,Help me look for it!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:03.24,0:04:05.20,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you can find it!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:06.12,0:04:07.41,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's following me, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:09.62,0:04:11.62,natsume,,0,0,0,,What are you looking for?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:11.62,0:04:13.42,natsume,,0,0,0,,What am I looking for?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:14.83,0:04:17.17,natsume,,0,0,0,,Something warm.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:17.17,0:04:21.01,natsume,,0,0,0,,Looking for something warm in all this snow?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:21.01,0:04:22.43,natsume,,0,0,0,,Are you cold?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:23.51,0:04:26.14,natsume,,0,0,0,,Well, shoot. This is about the best I can do.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:27.64,0:04:28.26,natsume,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:28.68,0:04:29.81,natsume,,0,0,0,,You can have this.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:34.52,0:04:35.69,natsume,,0,0,0,,Cold!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:36.73,0:04:38.57,natsume,,0,0,0,,Whoa! It's frozen!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:38.57,0:04:40.07,natsume,,0,0,0,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:40.07,0:04:42.99,natsume,,0,0,0,,If you don't keep your distance, you'll end up freezing me too.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:44.70,0:04:47.70,natsume,,0,0,0,,Something more sparkly.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.24,natsume,,0,0,0,,Sparkly?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:49.24,0:04:50.95,natsume,,0,0,0,,That isn't what you said before.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:52.66,0:04:55.83,natsume,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've spoken to a person.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:56.63,0:04:58.21,natsume,,0,0,0,,It feels strange.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:59.30,0:05:01.84,natsume,,0,0,0,,Was it something you lost?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:01.84,0:05:04.09,natsume,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it was around here?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:04.09,0:05:05.30,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:05.30,0:05:06.80,natsume,,0,0,0,,I can't remember.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:07.30,0:05:12.48,natsume,,0,0,0,,It was warm, sparkly, and smelled good.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:12.48,0:05:13.18,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:13.48,0:05:14.73,natsume,,0,0,0,,You can't remember?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:14.73,0:05:20.19,natsume,,0,0,0,,You mean you're looking for something with no idea what or where it is?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:20.69,0:05:24.20,natsume,,0,0,0,,I only know that I have to find it.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:24.20,0:05:26.45,natsume,,0,0,0,,I've never once forgotten that.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:27.32,0:05:29.70,natsume,,0,0,0,,I've even been looking for it in my dreams.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:30.24,0:05:31.95,natsume,,0,0,0,,Aren't you an oddball?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:33.45,0:05:34.91,natsume,,0,0,0,,Let's look for it together!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:34.91,0:05:37.83,natsume,,0,0,0,,You're looking for something too, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:37.83,0:05:39.75,natsume,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not looking for anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:39.75,0:05:40.84,natsume,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:40.84,0:05:45.30,natsume,,0,0,0,,I was under the impression that humans are generally in search of something.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:45.30,0:05:46.18,natsume,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:46.55,0:05:50.01,natsume,,0,0,0,,You're always looking for something or forgetting something.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:50.01,0:05:52.60,natsume,,0,0,0,,Humans are much stranger than I am.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:52.60,0:05:56.94,natsume,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm sorry to say that I can't help you unless you remember something.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:57.23,0:05:58.10,natsume,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:59.52,0:06:01.32,natsume,,0,0,0,,Wait, thin one!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.32,0:06:03.44,natsume,,0,0,0,,How cold can you be?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:03.44,0:06:05.69,natsume,,0,0,0,,Cold? You're the one who–
Dialogue: 5,0:06:11.28,0:06:12.70,natsume,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:12.70,0:06:14.79,natsume,,0,0,0,,What a strange guy.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:21.09,0:06:22.17,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:23.00,0:06:24.55,natsume,,0,0,0,,Shigeru-san?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:24.55,0:06:25.97,natsume,,0,0,0,,Takashi?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:25.97,0:06:28.26,natsume,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Something happen?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:28.26,0:06:32.10,natsume,,0,0,0,,No, uh... the snow just got me a little too excited.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:32.10,0:06:35.52,natsume,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that why you were running so fast?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:44.11,0:06:47.90,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it doesn't snow much around here.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:47.90,0:06:51.53,natsume,,0,0,0,,When I was a kid, I'd get all excited when it snowed like this.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:51.53,0:06:54.91,natsume,,0,0,0,,I had fun leaving footprints in the snow.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:55.20,0:07:01.33,natsume,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be the first one to leave my footprints in the snow, so I ran all over the place.{desperate is a too strong word "I was so desperate to be the first to leave a footprint somewhere that I ran around all over the place."}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:04.21,0:07:05.42,natsume,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:07.13,0:07:09.17,natsume,,0,0,0,,Apparently we're having hot pot tonight.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:09.17,0:07:11.18,natsume,,0,0,0,,Oh? Sounds good.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:12.64,0:07:14.64,natsume,,0,0,0,,Oh, you two came back together.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:14.64,0:07:16.18,natsume,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:16.64,0:07:18.18,natsume,,0,0,0,,Now, eat up.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:18.73,0:07:19.69,natsume,,0,0,0,,This looks great.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:19.69,0:07:20.31,natsume,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:21.48,0:07:22.56,natsume,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:30.49,0:07:32.49,natsume,,0,0,0,,Not again.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:32.74,0:07:35.24,natsume,,0,0,0,,What kind of a moron was it {\i1}this{\i} time?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:35.24,0:07:38.62,natsume,,0,0,0,,Not someone after the Book of Friends, I hope?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:38.62,0:07:39.87,natsume,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:40.46,0:07:41.75,natsume,,0,0,0,,You're drinking again?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:41.75,0:07:43.63,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hm? Snow is best watched with a drink in hand.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:43.63,0:07:45.25,natsume,,0,0,0,,But you're not even watching the snow.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:45.25,0:07:46.38,natsume,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:47.30,0:07:50.30,natsume,,0,0,0,,It didn't mistake me for Reiko-san or anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:50.30,0:07:53.39,natsume,,0,0,0,,And it didn't seem like its name was\Nin the Book of Friends, either.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:53.72,0:07:58.35,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hm? Did you say it was looking for something in the snow?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:58.35,0:08:00.68,natsume,,0,0,0,,Does it ring a bell, Sensei?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:00.68,0:08:05.48,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'm not really sure... Uh...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:06.23,0:08:07.90,natsume,,0,0,0,,I don't remember!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:07.90,0:08:09.99,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's because you've had too much to drink.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:11.28,0:08:15.87,natsume,,0,0,0,,My, my, I didn't think there would be such a beautiful spirit of a lady here–
Dialogue: 5,0:08:20.79,0:08:22.00,natsume,,0,0,0,,It looked like this.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:23.25,0:08:25.46,natsume,,0,0,0,,What's this dull looking thing supposed to be? {"half-wit" is not correct, it's more about a sluggish, not much moving and dull person}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:25.46,0:08:27.54,natsume,,0,0,0,,This fluffy thing is it.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:28.30,0:08:30.05,natsume,,0,0,0,,All right. It's time to get some sleep.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:30.05,0:08:33.05,natsume,,0,0,0,,No! I want to drink more! {"some" is not needed}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:39.68,0:08:42.31,natsume,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's still searching.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:42.60,0:08:43.52,natsume,,0,0,0,,All alone.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:43.52,0:08:48.32,natsume,,0,0,0,,I was under the impression that humans are generally in search of something.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:49.07,0:08:52.49,natsume,,0,0,0,,You're always looking for something or forgetting something.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:53.90,0:08:57.07,natsume,,0,0,0,,That might just be true.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:04.54,0:09:06.38,natsume,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:07.21,0:09:08.34,natsume,,0,0,0,,I can't see anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:08.88,0:09:11.34,natsume,,0,0,0,,What am I looking for?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:18.05,0:09:19.10,natsume,,0,0,0,,I have to find it.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:20.10,0:09:21.35,natsume,,0,0,0,,I have to find it.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:22.93,0:09:23.60,natsume,,0,0,0,,So cold.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:25.89,0:09:27.02,natsume,,0,0,0,,So cold.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:28.11,0:09:30.32,natsume,,0,0,0,,Way too cold!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:33.78,0:09:34.82,natsume,,0,0,0,,Fluffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:34.82,0:09:36.24,natsume,,0,0,0,,You followed me here?!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:36.24,0:09:38.03,natsume,,0,0,0,,Is that the– {sensei does not say "half-wit", bussari has no real meaning}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.03,0:09:39.66,natsume,,0,0,0,,What's with this chill in the air?!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:39.66,0:09:41.74,natsume,,0,0,0,,Get the heater, Natsume!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:41.74,0:09:43.50,natsume,,0,0,0,,J-Just its presence makes it cold!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:43.50,0:09:45.21,natsume,,0,0,0,,Where's my hot-water bottle?!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:45.21,0:09:48.25,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'm here to give this back to you, thin one.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:49.63,0:09:51.63,natsume,,0,0,0,,I-It's frozen solid!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:51.92,0:09:53.34,natsume,,0,0,0,,M-My scarf...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:53.34,0:09:55.51,natsume,,0,0,0,,You! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.84,0:09:57.38,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Sensei.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:57.38,0:09:59.51,natsume,,0,0,0,,It came all this way to give back the scarf.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:59.51,0:10:01.51,natsume,,0,0,0,,Let's hear it out.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.00,0:10:08.00,titlename,,0,0,0,,{\fs135\bord0\shad0\be1\c&H3A64DE&\pos(1248.6,200)}N{\c&H3676E2&}a{\c&H3188E6&}t{\c&H2D9BEA&}s{\c&H29ADEE&}u{\c&H24BFF2&}m{\c&H20D1F6&}e {\c&H3A64DE&}Y{\c&H3770E1&}u{\c&H347CE3&}u{\c&H3188E6&}j{\c&H2E94E9&}i{\c&H2CA1EB&}n{\c&H29ADEE&}c{\c&H26B9F1&}h{\c&H23C5F3&}o{\c&H20D1F6&}u
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:08.00,titlename-blur,,0,0,0,,{\p1\blur20\pos(1250,219)}m 0 0 s 1350 0 1350 150 0 150 c{\p0}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:08.98,0:10:11.61,natsume,,0,0,0,,So, do you think you'll be able to find it?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:11.61,0:10:12.52,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:13.03,0:10:15.57,natsume,,0,0,0,,I did find something warm.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:15.57,0:10:17.11,natsume,,0,0,0,,You found it?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:17.11,0:10:19.03,natsume,,0,0,0,,Right here in this house.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:19.03,0:10:19.78,natsume,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:19.78,0:10:23.54,natsume,,0,0,0,,I found so many warm things in this house!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:23.54,0:10:25.79,natsume,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:25.79,0:10:29.37,natsume,,0,0,0,,The things in this house couldn't be what you're searching for.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:30.63,0:10:31.29,natsume,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:32.84,0:10:34.55,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's so frozen that I can't tell what it is!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:34.92,0:10:36.84,natsume,,0,0,0,,So warm...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:37.59,0:10:40.14,natsume,,0,0,0,,But this isn't it.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:41.76,0:10:43.43,natsume,,0,0,0,,You trying to freeze us?!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:44.93,0:10:47.14,natsume,,0,0,0,,Don't get violent! {no word about a furball - "Be careful with that, you furball!"}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:47.14,0:10:49.10,natsume,,0,0,0,,Look who's talking!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:49.10,0:10:50.60,natsume,,0,0,0,,Listen up, Fluffy.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:50.60,0:10:52.15,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's something important to you, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:52.81,0:10:54.07,natsume,,0,0,0,,Very.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:54.07,0:10:59.07,natsume,,0,0,0,,Then try to remember what you're \Nsearching for, and where it could be.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:00.24,0:11:01.24,natsume,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:01.24,0:11:03.08,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:11.25,0:11:12.75,natsume,,0,0,0,,Don't doze off!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:13.75,0:11:14.92,natsume,,0,0,0,,I remember now!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:14.92,0:11:16.09,natsume,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:16.09,0:11:18.26,natsume,,0,0,0,,Something nostalgic.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:18.26,0:11:20.93,natsume,,0,0,0,,Nostalgic yet brand new.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:22.34,0:11:27.27,natsume,,0,0,0,,Why is it that you're looking for something that you don't even remember?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:27.27,0:11:28.85,natsume,,0,0,0,,I have to find it.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:29.73,0:11:30.98,natsume,,0,0,0,,I have to find it.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:32.02,0:11:33.40,natsume,,0,0,0,,I have to find it.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:34.56,0:11:35.32,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:42.16,0:11:44.91,natsume,,0,0,0,,I found something warm, but that wasn't it.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:44.91,0:11:47.29,natsume,,0,0,0,,I found something nostalgic, but that wasn't it.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:47.99,0:11:50.91,natsume,,0,0,0,,None of this is what I'm looking for.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:52.87,0:11:56.80,natsume,,0,0,0,,The strange boy asked me why I was looking for it.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:58.17,0:11:59.80,natsume,,0,0,0,,Why, indeed?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:00.76,0:12:03.55,natsume,,0,0,0,,I used to know the answer to that question.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:05.14,0:12:07.97,natsume,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure I'll figure it out when I find it.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:11.52,0:12:12.64,natsume,,0,0,0,,The snow's all piled up!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:16.73,0:12:17.90,natsume,,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:18.19,0:12:19.65,natsume,,0,0,0,,School's canceled today.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:19.65,0:12:22.15,natsume,,0,0,0,,Let's head out later and be the first\Nto leave footprints in the snow.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:22.95,0:12:25.16,natsume,,0,0,0,,What are you so excited about?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:26.12,0:12:27.41,natsume,,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:27.91,0:12:29.79,natsume,,0,0,0,,Whoa, it melted!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:32.75,0:12:34.79,natsume,,0,0,0,,What did it even–
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.29,0:12:39.30,sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.975\fax0.05\frz10.6\fscx72\fscy72\pos(1381.5,423)}Shigeru
Dialogue: 5,0:12:37.84,0:12:38.80,natsume,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:43.97,0:12:47.43,natsume,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was talking about warm, \Ngentle memories back then.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:56.48,0:13:01.53,natsume,,0,0,0,,With loving, warm people like \NShigeru-san and Touko-san around me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:03.32,sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.87\fax0.05\c&H0E120D&\fscx31\fscy31\pos(1146,802.5)\1a&H05&}Shigeru
Dialogue: 5,0:13:01.53,0:13:04.40,natsume,,0,0,0,,I was able to recover something I'd forgotten all about.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:04.40,0:13:05.36,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:05.36,0:13:12.08,natsume,,0,0,0,,Now, even the things I'd wanted \Nto forget feel precious to me.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:07.20,0:13:08.78,natsume,,0,0,0,,{\an8}See you later!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:19.84,0:13:24.72,natsume,,0,0,0,,I found that glove I lost in the field over there, but it was frozen solid!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:24.72,0:13:25.88,natsume,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:29.35,0:13:30.97,natsume,,0,0,0,,How far are we going?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:30.97,0:13:34.27,natsume,,0,0,0,,Well, we're trying to be the first to\N leave footprints somewhere,
Dialogue: 5,0:13:34.27,0:13:36.56,natsume,,0,0,0,,so we need to find a place nobody has set foot in.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:48.62,0:13:50.16,natsume,,0,0,0,,Marbles?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:50.16,0:13:52.45,natsume,,0,0,0,,What are you looking for?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:52.45,0:13:55.25,natsume,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're trying to help that... {removed "that pest!"}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:56.50,0:13:59.54,natsume,,0,0,0,,That fluffy thing is more dangerous than you think. {removed "half-wit"}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:59.54,0:14:05.59,natsume,,0,0,0,,If it so much as breathes on you and you get frozen solid, not even I would be able to help–
Dialogue: 5,0:14:07.97,0:14:09.59,natsume,,0,0,0,,Stop, you idiot!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:10.51,0:14:11.47,natsume,,0,0,0,,Something seems wrong.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:12.72,0:14:14.22,natsume,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Fluffy?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:15.23,0:14:16.64,natsume,,0,0,0,,Thin one.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:16.64,0:14:18.31,natsume,,0,0,0,,You must be tired.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:18.31,0:14:20.52,natsume,,0,0,0,,Have you been walking around looking for it all this while?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:20.52,0:14:22.11,natsume,,0,0,0,,I have to find it.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:22.11,0:14:23.82,natsume,,0,0,0,,I remembered.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:23.82,0:14:26.28,natsume,,0,0,0,,It'll vanish once it gets warmer!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:26.28,0:14:27.28,natsume,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:27.57,0:14:28.99,natsume,,0,0,0,,It will vanish!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:33.70,0:14:35.50,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hey! You all right?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:36.37,0:14:37.79,natsume,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:45.42,0:14:46.63,natsume,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? {removed "was that for}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:48.30,0:14:50.97,natsume,,0,0,0,,Forget it. I'm in a hurry.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:52.60,0:14:54.10,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Fluffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:54.47,0:14:55.56,natsume,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:02.65,0:15:03.86,natsume,,0,0,0,,Don't come crying to me later.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:11.36,0:15:13.07,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:15.24,0:15:18.20,natsume,,0,0,0,,Oh! Would you look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:21.62,sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.87\fax0.05\c&H192614&\1a&H05&\frz356.3\fscx46\fscy35\pos(1279.5,873)}Shigeru
Dialogue: 5,0:15:20.25,0:15:21.62,natsume,,0,0,0,,This is surprising.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:22.13,0:15:24.67,natsume,,0,0,0,,So you had held on to this too.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:24.67,0:15:27.30,natsume,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize what it was yesterday.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:27.30,0:15:28.88,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't you open it up?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:28.88,0:15:29.38,natsume,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:33.14,0:15:35.89,natsume,,0,0,0,,Just what you'd expect from a boy's treasure box.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:40.94,0:15:44.11,natsume,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'd completely forgotten about this.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:44.11,0:15:45.52,natsume,,0,0,0,,Brings back memories.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:46.11,0:15:49.61,natsume,,0,0,0,,These kind of things were still rare back then.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:54.74,0:15:56.24,natsume,,0,0,0,,I want Takashi to have this.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:56.24,0:15:58.37,natsume,,0,0,0,,Huh? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:58.37,0:16:00.79,natsume,,0,0,0,,On second thought, he's not a kid anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:00.79,0:16:01.83,natsume,,0,0,0,,I guess he doesn't need it.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:08.25,0:16:09.63,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's snowing again.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:11.34,0:16:13.93,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do you mean when you say it will vanish?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:14.72,0:16:15.55,natsume,,0,0,0,,I have to find it.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:16.05,0:16:18.56,natsume,,0,0,0,,You mean it'll melt like the snow?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:19.14,0:16:21.48,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hey, could what you're looking for be–
Dialogue: 5,0:16:21.48,0:16:23.94,natsume,,0,0,0,,What's all this racket?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:23.94,0:16:24.81,natsume,,0,0,0,,A human?!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.56,0:16:28.32,natsume,,0,0,0,,Not that hairy thing again! {removed "that creep"}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:28.32,0:16:30.82,natsume,,0,0,0,,I don't want it anywhere near me!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:31.78,0:16:35.45,natsume,,0,0,0,,Oh, please. One could swallow it whole.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:35.45,0:16:37.28,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's a real eyesore watching it loiter about.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:37.28,0:16:39.70,natsume,,0,0,0,,We should eat both of them.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:41.41,0:16:42.46,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:42.79,0:16:44.92,natsume,,0,0,0,,Watch your tongue, you lowlifes!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:44.92,0:16:45.83,natsume,,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:45.83,0:16:48.96,natsume,,0,0,0,,The cold makes me angry!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:52.76,0:16:54.97,natsume,,0,0,0,,This is my prey.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:54.97,0:16:59.51,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'll eat anyone who dares to lay a finger on it!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:05.31,0:17:07.44,natsume,,0,0,0,,Nothing good ever comes of this.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:07.44,0:17:08.44,natsume,,0,0,0,,We're going home, Natsume.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:08.82,0:17:10.48,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Sensei.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:10.48,0:17:16.91,natsume,,0,0,0,,but I kind of know how it feels to want to recover something you've forgotten.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:16.91,0:17:21.20,natsume,,0,0,0,,So I'd like to help look for it.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:26.58,0:17:30.96,natsume,,0,0,0,,Tell me, is the thing you are looking for really a physical entity?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:30.96,0:17:32.13,natsume,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:32.13,0:17:34.17,natsume,,0,0,0,,What else could it be?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:34.17,0:17:36.63,natsume,,0,0,0,,Like a memory or something.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:37.59,0:17:39.10,natsume,,0,0,0,,You're a strange one.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:39.10,0:17:41.01,natsume,,0,0,0,,And you say some funny things. {removed "silly", the snowman doesn't say silly}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:42.56,0:17:43.72,natsume,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:49.48,0:17:52.19,natsume,,0,0,0,,Fluffy, there's something on your chest.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:56.28,0:17:57.70,natsume,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:59.82,0:18:01.58,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's so warm!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:01.58,0:18:04.95,natsume,,0,0,0,,Oh, right! That's right!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:06.33,0:18:07.46,natsume,,0,0,0,,Fluffy?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:07.46,0:18:09.88,natsume,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a seed.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:10.71,0:18:11.46,natsume,,0,0,0,,A seed?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:13.63,0:18:20.80,natsume,,0,0,0,,These things exist in this world for hundreds of years, wandering about searching for it.{due to the prev. sentence, 'these things' can imply 'these creatures' whereas 'it' means 'the seeds'. }
Dialogue: 5,0:18:21.39,0:18:28.27,natsume,,0,0,0,,They know they're fated to look for it, but at the same time, they're also fated to forget all about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:32.06,0:18:39.49,natsume,,0,0,0,,But on one snowy day, it sprouts forth within their bodies, buds a flower, and vanishes.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:41.37,0:18:43.91,natsume,,0,0,0,,That is what Snow Flower is. {removed "snowflakes."}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:48.50,0:18:50.50,natsume,,0,0,0,,I've remembered it all.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:52.25,0:18:55.80,natsume,,0,0,0,,I was meant to become what I am now.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:01.47,0:19:04.31,natsume,,0,0,0,,And once that flower blooms...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:05.26,0:19:09.56,natsume,,0,0,0,,So all this while, she was looking for something that would make her disappear?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:09.56,0:19:10.56,natsume,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:16.03,0:19:17.28,natsume,,0,0,0,,She's vanishing!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:17.28,0:19:18.28,natsume,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:19.99,0:19:23.66,natsume,,0,0,0,,Thank you for finding it for me, strange guy.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:23.66,0:19:25.74,natsume,,0,0,0,,You strange, lovely guy.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:27.83,0:19:30.00,natsume,,0,0,0,,Don't look so sad.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:30.54,0:19:33.50,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll find what you're looking for as well.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:34.84,0:19:36.25,natsume,,0,0,0,,One day.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:50.85,0:19:52.52,natsume,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, Natsume.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:53.15,0:19:58.19,natsume,,0,0,0,,I hear that not even many spirits get to see this flower.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:58.19,0:20:03.32,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it means something good that we both got to see it.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:03.32,0:20:04.41,natsume,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:04.41,0:20:05.32,natsume,,0,0,0,,Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:07.41,0:20:11.50,natsume,,0,0,0,,Snow Flower may have vanished but a faint fragrance still lingered in the air–{replaced The snowflakes with Snow Flower}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:12.16,0:20:15.67,natsume,,0,0,0,,the scent of a spring yet to come.{i can't think of a better way to phrase this line. "the scent of spring, for which there's still some time left"}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:17.84,0:20:19.26,natsume,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:19.92,0:20:21.30,natsume,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:21.30,0:20:27.47,natsume,,0,0,0,,You see, I found Shigeru-san's childhood treasure box while I was cleaning the storeroom.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:27.47,0:20:29.68,natsume,,0,0,0,,Oh, you did?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:30.02,0:20:33.44,natsume,,0,0,0,,He said he wants you to have this.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:41.82,0:20:46.70,natsume,,0,0,0,,Snow Flower, I don't know what I'm looking for either. {removed "Snowflake"}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:47.83,0:20:50.79,natsume,,0,0,0,,I don't know what I'll find in the future.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:52.12,0:20:55.83,natsume,,0,0,0,,Or if I'll be able to keep the memories of the things I find.
